The players take it in turns to choose one block and "eat it" (remove from the board), together with those that are below it and to its right. The top left block is "poisoned" and the player who eats this loses. The board has 4 rows. The board has 5 columns.
(game "Chomp" (players 2) (equipment {(board (rectangle 4 5)) (piece "Chocolate" Shared)}) (rules (start (place "Chocolate" (sites Board))) (play (move Remove (sites Occupied by:Shared) (then (forEach Site (sites Occupied by:Shared) (if (and (ge (row of:(last To)) (row of:(site))) (le (column of:(last To)) (column of:(site)))) (remove (site))))))) (end (if (is In (last To) (intersection (sites Top) (sites Left))) (result Mover Loss))))) 
